comment: Payton (ORL) makes contact with Williams' (LAL) arm, affecting his jump shot.
Harris (ORL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Randle's (LAL) drive to the basket.
Hibbert (LAL) and Vucevic (ORL) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Harris (ORL) cleanly blocks Randle's (LAL) jump shot.
Vucevic (ORL) does not touch the ball until it is outside of the cylinder.
The shot by Williams (LAL) does not hit the rim and a 24 Second Violation is correctly called.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court of a 24 Second Violation was upheld.
As Fournier (ORL) cuts toward the rim and World Peace (LAL) steps backwards, the two connect and fall, but the contact is incidental to their progress and not enough to warrant a foul.

After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Vucevic's (ORL) shot was released prior to the clock expiring was upheld.
